title: Sue Bird
description: Samantha Bee sits down with WNBA star and style icon Sue Bird to talk about becoming an activist, why we'd all be better off if the WNBA was in charge of the country, what gives athletes a "cool factor" and if she and Megan Rapinoe will ever get into politics.
author: fullrelease@sambee.com (Samantha Bee & Earwolf)
